data.description: Super cute 2-bedroom, 1-bath ranch-style house with a basement and located in the heart of Frankfort. This home features a private backyard with a side patio that offers a serene and comfortable outdoor space for enjoying a morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends and family. The convenient location is close to downtown so shopping, restaurants, coffee shops, and more are just a stroll or bike ride away. Don't miss the opportunity to make this one yours.
